{"tid":2101574,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[曼聯又贏]曼聯又創兩大英超紀錄：史上單賽季獲12碼數創新高","createTime":"2020-07-10T02:03:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T02:18:02.000Z","uid":103207,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5f34d290742ceecd3d7d28d72c9cae0c339ea275","tid":2101574,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:03:37.000Z","msg":"曼聯3比0擊敗阿士東維拉，同時創造了英超的兩個紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n  首先，曼聯成為了<span class=\"red\">歷史上第一支連續4場比賽都以3球或者3球以上取勝的球隊</span>。<br />\n<br />\n  在今場3比0之前，曼聯5比2大勝般尼茅夫，3比0擊敗白禮頓，3比0詹笙錫菲聯聯隊，連續4場大捷，展現出曼聯良好的形勢，以及球隊爆棚的信心。<br />\n<br />\n  其次，曼聯今場由般奴-費南迪斯製造12碼並罰進，<span class=\"red\">今季至今紅魔在英超中已拿到了13個12碼，這是歷史上單賽季獲得12碼數的新紀錄。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1214b11fa4d1e23efa0684085ec1e1ad5db63e16","tid":2101574,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:05:44.000Z","msg":"球技唔夠，只能用犯規戰術<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d83845fb4af24842f572437cd4d7a13400b5af","tid":2101574,"uid":103207,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1214b11fa4d1e23efa0684085ec1e1ad5db63e16","tid":2101574,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:05:44.000Z","msg":"球技唔夠，只能用犯規戰術<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:12:08.000Z","msg":"演技撘夠"},{"pid":"d1cc6571da42fd7f2644bbcd934e677267db4169","tid":2101574,"uid":73340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:18:02.000Z","msg":"自從無左超新星 連加特爵士之後<br />\n班波踢得差左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}